# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Released]
## [0.1.2] - 29-03-2022
### Add
- Add button re-download anime if download are stop

### Fixed
- when download is filed, bar progress is red with write 'filed' instead of percentual with value 100%
- when download is completed, bar progress is green with write 'completed' instead of percentual
- Resolve problem open file

### Changed
- DownloadService start timeout 0 to max limit defined and print log if error download with attempts remains, if download is success reset timeout

## [0.1.1] - 29-03-2022
### Added
- new button into bar search for get all anime

### Changed
- color buttons into bar search


## [0.1.0] - 27-03-2022
### Version Stable